{"tid":685301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"越南女整容嫁富二代 老公5個月即出軌","createTime":"2018-05-31T10:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T10:59:22.000Z","uid":75969,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c03318d02e63a208200b8730fada13edaa945ae3","tid":685301,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180531/_2018053114470385324.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180531%2F_2018053114470385324.jpg&h=b0d95051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">越南女子郭金鳳整容前後判若兩人。網圖</span><br />\n<br />\n越南一名女子經常在相睇時被對方嫌棄長得醜，過於傷心的她花費3億越南盾（約10萬港元）整容，一年後便嫁給富二代，但這段婚姻只維持了5個月，令她感歎「男人承諾很廉價」！<br />\n<br />\n該名越南女子郭金鳳（Qu&aacute;ch Kim Phượng）天生顏值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 較輸蝕，因此異性緣幾乎是零。其父母一直擔心她沒有男朋友，於是透過不少方法為郭金鳳安排相睇，希望女兒可以早日出嫁。但郭金鳳每次相睇都不太如意，常被對方嫌棄外貌，各種針對外貌的批評令她格外傷心。<br />\n<br />\n為增強自信，郭金鳳決定到醫院整容及做牙齒矯正手術，前後花費了3億越南盾，令其不完美的嘴唇及鼻子，瞬間變得漂亮起來，而臉上的痘印亦全部消去，在路上亦會有高回頭率，高顏值漸漸令她奪回自信心。<br />\n<br />\n郭金鳳在整容後又開始繼續相睇，在一次相睇中，她遇上了一名富二代，交談過後因非常合拍而相戀，不到半年兩人便結婚，令郭金鳳相信自己是個幸運女孩，婚姻一定會非常美滿。可惜天意弄人，兩人的婚姻並不幸福，丈夫在婚後開始出軌，更邀約不少女性外出喝酒，即使受到妻子的責備，亦未從放在心上，於是郭金鳳決定結束這五個月的婚姻，即使兩人已育有一名女兒。<br />\n<br />\n受傷的郭金鳳感歎，「這個童話故事很現實，但我一點也不敢相信。男人的承諾真的不要聽，很廉價」。雖然郭金鳳成為了單親媽媽，但幸而不久後她就遇上了現任丈夫，重新開始新一段婚姻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180531/_2018053114470370177.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180531%2F_2018053114470370177.jpg&h=73f7f1f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180531/_2018053114470727110.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180531%2F_2018053114470727110.jpg&h=7b098965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/729361\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F729361&d=kAOJYc4N%2BiwnhVVS4iNskARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ff18ebf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F729361&h=720b23bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/729361</a>"},{"pid":"7c23b6c2a3268be4ca2126093e2d00afd5779687","tid":685301,"uid":87613,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"個鼻好fail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c7bc4b175ab4b9df9e1818d78847928c064cdc","tid":685301,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:12:32.000Z","msg":"自己整完容眲人就冇問題<br />\n條仔俾你眲完飛你就唔得<br />\n又要做雞又要貞節牌坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7a0a3417723e3c521e88b0e4e336fad72b9fdc","tid":685301,"uid":39855,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:14:23.000Z","msg":"5個月婚姻，有個女，完！"},{"pid":"1573d8ec3143702f1bc37b119e0a9727fccc2f65","tid":685301,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e7a0a3417723e3c521e88b0e4e336fad72b9fdc","tid":685301,"uid":39855,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:14:23.000Z","msg":"5個月婚姻，有個女，完！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:15:31.000Z","msg":"我都睇到r 晒頭"},{"pid":"fb3336ccf57d837f9b3f69f8c157498f1f564835","tid":685301,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:16:58.000Z","msg":"鼻頭整到幾靚 鼻翼都呃唔到人"},{"pid":"0b3117a1447015430744cb9f149a086dee112a85","tid":685301,"uid":154186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61